{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Fire Goat|kanji=丁未|romaji=hinoto hitsuji|onyomi=teibi|p=dīwèi|w=ting-wei|mi=tʰiŋ⁵³ weɪ̯|y=deng1 mei6|j=deng1 mei6|ci=tɛŋ mei|mc=tæŋ mei|oc-bs=tæŋ mei}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yin Fire Goat also known as  Teibi''' (丁未) (ひのとひつじ、ていかのひつじ、ていび) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 44th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Bingwu|ja|丙午|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Wushen|ja|戊申|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Fire|ja|火|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Mei|ja|未|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fire generates Earth).

== Years of Teibi ==
A Common Era year that leaves a remainder of 47 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of Teibi.
