=== Events ===
* The conflict in {{ill|587 AD|ja|587th year|12=draft|12=draft}} between the {{ill|Soga clan|ja|蘇我氏|12=draft|12=draft}} and the {{ill|Mononobe clan|ja|物部氏|12=draft|12=draft}} is known as the {{ill|Teibi Rebellion|ja|丁未の乱|12=draft|12=draft}}.

== Months of Teibi ==
In a Common Era year, if the final digit is 2 or 7 (that is, when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft}}), then {{ill|June|ja|6月|12=draft|12=draft}} becomes the {{ill|Month|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|12=draft|12=draft}} of Teibi. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Shōsho|ja|小暑|lt=Shōsho|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Rittō|ja|立秋|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

== Days of Teibi ==
=== Day Selection ===
A day of Teibi is the 15th day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft}}.
