=== Events ===
* The conflict in {{ill|587 AD|ja|587th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} between the {{ill|Soga clan|ja|蘇我氏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the {{ill|Mononobe clan|ja|物部氏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is known as the {{ill|Teibi Rebellion|ja|丁未の乱|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

== Months of Teibi ==
In a Common Era year, if the final digit is 2 or 7 (that is, when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), then {{ill|June|ja|6月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} becomes the {{ill|Month|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of Teibi. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Shōsho|ja|小暑|lt=Shōsho|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Rittō|ja|立秋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.

== Days of Teibi ==
=== Day Selection ===
A day of Teibi is the 15th day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
