47 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2507 AD|ja|2507年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2507|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2507 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2567 AD|ja|2567年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2567|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2567 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2627 AD|ja|2627年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2627|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2627 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2687 AD|ja|2687年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2687|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2687 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2747 AD|ja|2747年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2747|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2747 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2807 AD|ja|2807年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2807|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2807 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2867 AD|ja|2867年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2867|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2867 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2927 AD|ja|2927年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2927|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2927 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2987 AD|ja|2987年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2987|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2987 AD|qq=}} |}
=== Events === * The conflict in [[:en:587|587 AD]] between the [[:en:Soga clan|Soga clan]] and the [[:en:Mononobe clan|Mononobe clan]] is known as the [[:en:Soga–Mononobe conflict|Teibi Rebellion]].
== Months of Teibi == In a Common Era year, if the final digit is 2 or 7 (that is, when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), then [[:en:June|June]] becomes the [[:en:Month|Month]] of Teibi. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Xiaoshu|Shōsho]] until the day before [[:en:Liqiu|Rittō]]) as applicable.
== Days of Teibi == === Day Selection === A day of Teibi is the 15th day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Heaven, One Heaven|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Heaven, One Heaven|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
